title.narrative: Partnership for Transforming Health Systems 2 - Procurement of Services

description.narrative: This activity (Partnership for Transforming Health Systems 2 - Procurement of Services) is a component of Partnership for Transforming Health Systems 2 reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £129,783,220. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Health policy and administrative management, Basic health care, Infectious disease control, Health education, Health personnel development, Reproductive health care, Public finance management (PFM), Democratic participation and civil society. , with the following implementing partners: Abt Associates Inc, Baker Tilly Nigeria, Crown Agents Limited, DAI Europe, Mott MacDonald Limited, Oxford Policy Management. The start date is 01-10-2008 and the end date is 31-10-2016.
